request.description:
After adding a product to the cart with the default value, user can update the `cart_item_quantity` and `total_installment` value. User will be notified about at least how much money they should pay for each installment if they tried to pay less. After paying the first installment, user can't update the update the `cart_item_quantity` and `total_installment` value again. Only they can update the value of `paid_amount`

Customer can choose in how many installment (total_installment = n) he/she wants to pay the total bill.

Pass id: /carts/cart-item/{cart-item-id}

